        <mj-text font-size="18px" color="#0082c8" font-family="helvetica">
          Submission
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-size="14px" line-height="120%" font-family="helvetica">
        We elicit the following types of papers:
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Research papers (8 pages inc. references)</strong>: technical research, experience reports, empirical studies, etc.</li>
            <li><strong>Position papers (2 pages inc. references)</strong>: well-argued position or work in progress.</li>
          </ul>
        Submissions can be made via the submission website: <a href="https://apr20.hotcrp.com">https://apr20.hotcrp.com</a>.        
